LICENSE HISTORY

This project was originally released under AGPL-3.0-or-later to match the
original MATLAB repository's license. It was re-licensed to MIT with explicit
written permission from the original authors (Keenan Crane, March 2026).

The optional quantization dependency (pyquantization) remains under AGPL-3.0
as it wraps third-party code with that license.

---

NOTE ON OPTIONAL DEPENDENCIES

The optional `pyquantization` package (installed via `pip install .[quantization]`)
is licensed under AGPL-3.0-or-later. If you use the quantization feature, the
AGPL terms apply to that component. The core RSP code in this repository is MIT.
